midwives-voices-subtext: Yebisabisaa awogyefo a wɔwɔ wiase nyinaa asɛm yi sɛ: “Dɛn na wopɛ paa wɔ wo dwumadi sɛ awogyefo no mu?”
pmnch-subtext: Yɛma wo akwaaba ba "Nea Mmabun Pɛ" Dashboard no so! Saa nkitahodi adwinnade yi ma mmuae ne nhumu a yɛreboaboa ano afi mmerante ne mmabaa a wɔadi mfe 10-24 hɔ wɔ wiase nyinaa no ho mfonini a wɔde aniwa hu. Adeyɛ no mu ade titiriw ne asɛmmisa a wɔabue ano: "Sɛ mɛma me yiyedi atu mpɔn no, mepɛ...". Mmabun a wofi wiase nyinaa abua eyi, na wɔama yɛn nhumu soronko wɔ wɔn ahiade, anidaso, ne wɔn apɛde ahorow ho. Hwehwɛ data no mu, hu nsɛm a ɛwɔ akontaabu no akyi, na kɔka yɛn ho ma yɛma mmerante ne mmabaa ɔpepepem 1.8 nne yɛ kɛse wɔ wiase nyinaa. Sɛ wopɛ sɛ wosua pii fa ɔsatuo no ho a, kɔ http://www.1point8.org.
